  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362400/extras/1f1b5825e5d7a1e1e4da61dccd7decf6.poster.avif?t=1671623653\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362400/extras/1f1b5825e5d7a1e1e4da61dccd7decf6.webm?t=1671623653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362400/extras/1f1b5825e5d7a1e1e4da61dccd7decf6.mp4?t=1671623653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>There are other rulers sitting on <i>your</i> planet? Time to intervene!</strong><br><br>In this local couch brawler, you and up to three friends take on the role of a ruler in order to control the planets. In order to achieve this goal, however, your fellow combatants must leave the planet - one way or another. Each of the planets will react differently during your battle. Secure the last place on our shrinking Earth, be the only one to survive the fast ride on Mercury and be the last one to not get confused on dusty Mars - because the magnificent crown only fits on one head.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362400/extras/c90ef2c923f61732d2413a701a15a944.poster.avif?t=1671623653\" width=616 height=137 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362400/extras/c90ef2c923f61732d2413a701a15a944.webm?t=1671623653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose from over 20 historically influential figures.<br></li><li>Fight on 11 planets with different gameplay mechanics.<br></li><li>Play with up to 3 friends.<br></li><li>Become the number one ruler in your living room.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362400/extras/564cbe944357fbc5a23a1fb7b60078f3.poster.avif?t=1671623653\" width=616 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362400/extras/564cbe944357fbc5a23a1fb7b60078f3.webm?t=1671623653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362400/extras/564cbe944357fbc5a23a1fb7b60078f3.mp4?t=1671623653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
